<br />

<br />
Those pieces will pump up ur HP not to badly within range from the gear ur wearing now.
<br />

<br />
Once obtained some plate pieces try to sell ur freecoming slots and try grab some bloodmetal earrings and of or farm the PoTa piggie for the Earring of Rage.
<br />

<br />
And if ya wanna farm there either way u can make some nice cash there if ur lucky.
<br />

<br />
But from my view atm there are some pieces u can update from bazaar but save urself the cash since u dont wanna spend to much and farm bot and PoTa for now and maybe during raids upcoming some nice drops will get to you.
