				<td colspan="2"><span>Couple suggestions.
<br />

<br />
Since you've been doing some GoD farming, move back a step to the sewers.  In Lair, the Sludge-Eating Fly drops Pitted Vambraces fairly often, nice upgrade.  Hit Plant and head for Kril V'Lak for the Veil of Mist.  While you're there, you'll have a good chance at getting War March of the Mastruq, if you don't have it already.
<br />

<br />
If you have plat to burn (or feel like doing some hard ldons, which I'd suggest), go for Bloodied Boots of Dark Rites (MM), Warlord's Steel Gauntlets (Rujark), and the previously mentioned Mana-Threaded Bone Bracelet.  Also in those hard ldon's, you could snag a Trueborn Elite Ring from MM.  It all depends on how you wanna spend your time. <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" /></span></td>
			</tr><tr>
